parameters:
\nc<Senpai>That customer is quite the masochist, so don't hesitate to
be rough with him.

\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>Eeeeh... Masochist, as in S&M? I've never done anything like
that before...

\nc<Senpai>Oh, it's fine. When I say violence, I mostly mean verbal
abuse. He's not that difficult a customer.

\nc<Senpai>The more you insult him, the more excited he gets, so give
it your best. Think of it as an opportunity to vent your
daily stress.
\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>I really don't have confidence in this though...
